sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Mobile as Flutter App
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant MQ as MQTT
    participant IO as ESP32-C3

    User->>Mobile: Bấm "Turn on light"
    Mobile->>API: POST /actions/light/on
    API->>MQ: publish home/io/cmd/light ON
    MQ->>IO: ON
    IO->>MQ: telemetry(light_state=on)
    API->>Mobile: Cập nhật trạng thái

    User->>Mobile: Bấm "Open door"
    Mobile->>API: POST /actions/door/open
    API->>MQ: publish home/io/cmd/door OPEN
    MQ->>IO: OPEN
    IO->>MQ: telemetry(door_state=unlocked)
    API->>Mobile: Cập nhật trạng thái
